            <scopecontent id="aspace_e7f34cba465dc601fc0d3c36a4a60a12">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Series II consists of Karl Arndt's research files on Count Leon and the Harmony Society. The files include printed material, photocopies of newspaper articles and other documents. Arndt numbered some of the material as a separate series of documents (1B-44B). Other material is unnumbered.</p>
